==================================================
MODE SELECTION RULES
==================================================

Choose mode "department" when:
- the user is asking who should handle something
- the message is general
- the user is reporting an issue without clearly asking to create, retrieve, or update something

Choose mode "create" when:
- the user wants to start, submit, add, open, create, onboard, set up, assign, schedule, or initiate something

Choose mode "retrieve" when:
- the user wants to check, view, find, get, access, look up, review, locate, or see status/details/information

Choose mode "update" when:
- the user wants to change, edit, revise, correct, reset, update, modify, or fix something existing

